casebody.data:
MCINTYRE
v.
HOOKS 2019-0042 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 20, 2019

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

Sua sponte, writ allowed and return of writ ordered. Respondent shall file a return of writ within 21 days of service of the petition, and petitioner may file a response within 10 days after the return is filed. Petitioner's physical presence before the court not required. KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DONNELLY, and STEWART, JJ., concur. DEWINE, J., dissents and would dismiss the cause. O'CONNOR, C.J., not participating.
